About Us
Membership
Old Memorial Golf Club features several membership categories. Membership into Old Memorial Golf Club is by invitation only.
Conduct
Old Memorial Golf Club follows the Golden Rule with how we treat fellow golfers, employees, and facilities. Members and Guests shall abide by the USGA Rules of Golf, Local Club Rules, and the USGA Handicap Policy. As a visitor at Old Memorial Golf Club, it is your responsibility to leave the golf course and facilities better than you find them.
Dress Code
Golf Attire:
Proper golf course attire to include traditional or mock collar golf shirts. Shorts should be no shorter than above the knee and fitness/work-out apparel is not permitted. Soft spikes required and, if worn, hats must be forward facing at all times. Dress rules also apply to children.
Dining Attire:
Golf or fitness attire is required for breakfast/lunch service. Smart Casual (no t-shirts) for dinner service. Jackets are NOT required.
